---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Products — ruuley" canonical="/en/products/">
  <section class="hero container">
    <h1>Products</h1>
    <p>Integrated toolset supporting JSON-IR from editing to distribution</p>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Validation Gate</h3>
        <p><strong>Unified Diagnostics and Quality Assurance</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Multi-layered quality checks</li>
          <li>Automated verification through CI/CD integration</li>
          <li>Backend-specific compatibility assessment</li>
          <li>Structured diagnostic reports</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Integration Bundler</h3>
        <p><strong>Multi-Article Integration and Auditing</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Automatic integration of multiple documents</li>
          <li>Consistency checks for vocabulary and concepts</li>
          <li>Maintenance of traceability</li>
          <li>Comprehensive audit reports</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Editor</h3>
        <p><strong>Intuitive Editing Experience</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Support for latest specifications</li>
          <li>Automatic validation on save</li>
          <li>Error correction support</li>
          <li>Traceability visualization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Trace & Witness</h3>
        <p><strong>Traceability Visualization</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Coverage visualization</li>
          <li>Consistency verification</li>
          <li>Correspondence mapping</li>
          <li>Navigation features</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Verification Suite</h3>
        <p><strong>Round-Trip Verification</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Completeness checks</li>
          <li>Automatic correction suggestions</li>
          <li>Completion from external data</li>
          <li>Issue resolution support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>AI Copilot (β)</h3>
        <p><strong>Intelligent Editing Support</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Concept suggestions and optimization</li>
          <li>Automatic completion of missing information</li>
          <li>Safety-focused evaluation</li>
          <li><a href="/en/ai/">Learn more →</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>Integrated Workflow</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>These tools work together to provide a seamless workflow from editing to distribution:</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Editing</strong>: Editing with an intuitive editor</li>
        <li><strong>Verification</strong>: Automatic quality checks</li>
        <li><strong>Integration</strong>: Integration of multiple documents</li>
        <li><strong>Auditing</strong>: Traceability verification</li>
        <li><strong>Distribution</strong>: Code generation and deployment</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

